posts.com:
i said a couple weeks ago that i would rate modern warfare 2 maps so im finally getting around to it
though im only gonna do ones that ive played on enough and half-ass it probably idk
anyway i pick afghan for the first because i hate it enough
its a shitty map but also for some reason i dont really mind playing in it ill get to that later
its just too open and too big
u get faggots shooting at u from the other side of the map from nowhere while you dont have anybody on ur team anywhere near you
like its genuinely rare to see teammates on that map if ur not right at the spawn wave
ok maybe not but it feels like it
anyhow, despite being open its still full of bottlenecks you have to walk through to get to the middle or where anybody is
and anybody can just camp those bottlenecks from a million miles away because theres so little cover, so they do
it feels like you just have to get lucky to be able to walk around, i probably havent ever gotten more than care package on afghan ever in my life cause if you actually move around youre guaranteed to die to some retard from the other side of the map
i think all it comes down to is just who sees who first
because its so open and anybody can take pretty much any sightline, most fights are just you getting killed before even seeing the person who shot u, or even if you noticed them it being too late
sure the first shot advantage is a thing in any map, but in ones like afghan its different because youre simply not gonna be able to react to whos shooting
if its an overall smaller one like skidrow then even if you get shot first then you have a chance of reacting in time and winning still
but in afghan whoever is shooting you is probably going to be a speck on your screen and youll be dead before youre even able to notice them, all it comes down to is who notices the other one first, its like playing arma in cod
ig this really only applies to the middle of the map but the rest of it is no less cancer

posts.name: Madokanon
posts.com:
the cliffside is retarded because every single time the person who loses is the one that rushes
its designed in a way so that there really is not much way for you to win if you rush and try to kill whoevers watching the corners ur coming from and that sucks, depending on what side youre from you have to be moving upwards or down and that both makes it way easier for you to get shot and shoot at whoevers there
also since its an open area its really easy to just get flashed/semtexed and thats cancer
ive never seen anybody manage to move up the cliffside if there were more than one person they have to fight lol
u either try to stun/catch people off guard or die so its just a more uncomfortable hallway basically
little chokepoints like that are in a lot of maps sure but they tend to be in a shape so that the rusher has a chance of winning still, not here
anyhow its a smaller chunk of the map so it wouldnt even really matter either way
the grassy side is also shit, u barely fight anyone in it because of how the spawns are and if you do theyre going to kill you because its fucking impossible to see from the retarded head-high bushes they decided to place in there, and thats assuming you dont get killed the instant u arrive there from a dude standing on high ground or peeking it from halfway across the map
so basically both other sides of the map besides the middle are just camping spots and thats retarded. only way for u to move is to depend on luck and have nobody looking where ur coming from because ur most likely going to die if they are, its just the way afghan is designed
the grassy side also leads into the bunkers which are total aids
its a high-ground camping spot thats hard to take shots at, i mean yeah i guess thats what the purpose a mg bunker serves in real life but its not really fun to play against in a cod map lol

posts.name: Madokanon
posts.com:
also i have no idea why but somebody decided itd be a good idea to make it really hard to see the people inside the bunker if ur looking from the outside, especially if youre far away, while the people in the bunker have perfect visibility
its really easy for them to kill u before you even notice the dark figure moving god i hate it
idk how it looks in the normal game because i play with the fps booster in iw4x but i really doubt its any better
and its really easy for the person in the bunker to get in cover instantly if they get shot, while the person outside is probably gonna get raped instantly after they even try to shoot at the bunker guy
ya there is the path from the grassy side u can use to get in the bunker but its so tight that its really easy for the camper inside the bunker to deny anyone trying to get from there
you can kill them eventually if you try hard enough to i guess, but it doesnt make it any less cancer
oh and theres the adjacent bunker which is really underrated, i think it may be better than the other one but people just dont realize lol, i rarely go into the bunkers when i play that map cause i dont suck enough dicks but when i do its that one
and now im remembering i did actually get a care package on that map and it was because of that bunker so yeah
overall, it feels like the whole map is just completely designed around sniper faggotry so any other kind of playstyle is not fun to play with, smgs are borderline useless and with ars it just comes back to whoever sees who first, and u need to use an accurate one at that. the most ull get out of it is winning fights in the sides of the map but its not really much fun either to be walking around in them, just as bad as getting sniped in the middle
so it really gimps you and forces u to use certain weapons to do well and i dont think thats good in a map

posts.name: Madokanon
posts.com:
anyway
like i said before for some reason i dont really mind it that much still
which might come down to the masochism i have with cod but eh, i cant even really get that out of it
its not exactly like rust, where its so fucking terrible that u have to embrace the aids and enjoy it for that
in afghan its more like that torture method where they dip you in water with a rope and out of it over and over again
like you get too many glimpses of hope instead of being bombarded with cancer, its gonna make you think ur okay for a second before you go back to being killed from the other side of the map, i swear ive never had a map question my abilities in a game more than this one
oh well, either way, i used to really wanna die whenever afghan came on and i still do but its less than before
at least its still a bit of fun to set tactical inserts inside the airplane in the middle that people rarely go into, or sit on some rocks near the cave entrances because people rarely look up
oh and its one of those maps where if anyone gets a chopper gunner then u cant play anymore so that sucks
if you know how it feels like to instantly stop actually trying to play once you see a map loading then then i get that in this one
anyway idk maybe its just me
cause i still see people doing good in this map somehow
do they know something i dont and am i just really bad at mw2 i dont know
maybe but u probably have to be really gay to do good at this map so i guess its okay that i cant
u know now im thinking next time i play in it, like a few months from now probably, im just gonna bunker camp cause i dont care this shithole doesnt deserve any better
o well i dont think i explained very well what i hate about it, but im gonna leave it at that
my overall rating is - map that makes me wanna uninstall the game after the match is over/10
im gonna get some tea then lay down and read something for a bit then maybe go for another one or just sleep lol
